  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You mastered your beast completely and are willing to sacrifice it for power. While in Baryon Mode, you are locked in a constant struggle, trying to outlive your Sealed Beast. You forcibly combine your life forces, receiving a power greater than the sum of its parts.</p><p>At the start of each turn that you are in Baryon Mode, you must reduce your Maximum Hit Points by 1d10 and your beast's Maximum Twisted Chakra by 4d10. Add the results together, you gain an amount of Fusion Chakra equal to half of the result, replacing any Fusion Chakra you might already have. You can spend Fusion Chakra as you would normal chakra.</p><p>If your Maximum Hit Points are reduced to 0, you die and your Sealed Beast is released upon the world. Alternatively, if your Sealed Beast's Maximum Twisted Chakra is reduced to 0 first, you lose this Class Mod as the beast is consumed as fuel by your seal.</p><p>Maximum Hit Points and Twisted Chakra lost through Sacrificial Beast can be regained by spending Downtime to recover both at a rate of 5 Maximum Hit Points and Twisted Chakra per week.</p>",
